      "message_content": "Hey devs 👋\n\nBuilt something that might be useful if you're running ElizaOS agents in production — **AgentAudit**: immutable on-chain audit logs for AI agents, EU AI Act compliant.\n\nOne SDK call logs any agent action directly to the blockchain — tamper-proof, timestamped, permanently auditable:\n\n```ts\nawait audit.log({\n  action: 'TRANSFER_APPROVED',\n  metadata: JSON.stringify({ amount: '100 USDC', recipient: '0x...' }),\n});\n```\n\n✅ Live on Arbitrum Sepolia: `0x25ac2ab1369001F9C847e65f010B6e4f4340d78a`\n✅ Live on Mantle Sepolia: `0x25ac2ab1369001F9C847e65f010B6e4f4340d78a`\n✅ TypeScript SDK ready\n🔌 ElizaOS plugin — coming this week\n\nGitHub: https://github.com/agentauditAI/AgentAudit\n\nWould love feedback from anyone building autonomous agents that touch real transactions. Happy to collab on the ElizaOS plugin 🤝"
